content.rendered:
Directed by Abhishek Kapoor

Written by Kanika Dhillon. Kanika Dhillon

Cast Sushant Singh Rajput (Mansoor Khan). Sara Ali Khan (Mandakini aka Mukku). Nitish Bharadwaj (Briraaj). Alka Amin (Mansoor’s Mother). Sonali Sachdev (Lata – Mukku’s Mother). Pooja Gaur (Brinda (as Pooja Gor)). Nishant Dahiya (Kullu). Arun Bali (Chief Purohit). Shahab Ali (Mustafa – Mansoor’s Father). Sunita Rajwar (Dadoo – The Nagging Pilgrim). Mahendra Mewati (Mental Baba). Vinamra Pancharia (Afzar). Mir Sarwar (Bashir). Basu Soni (Gullu). Tarun Gahlot (Kailash). Faiz Khan (Hemchand). Amaan Iqbal (Bala). Sharad Vyas (Himalaya Tyagi). Anil Khopkar (Pt. Durge). Akshay Bhat (Debu). Pushkin Puri (Bala’s Father). Priyanka Tiwari (Gullu’s Wife). Simaran Sabharwal (Afzar’s Wife). Aarav Malhotra (Young Mansoor). Ajitesh Gupta (Assistant at Weather Department). Kumar Saurabh (Assistant at Weather Department). Harish Khandal (Rescue Pilot). Bhupesh Bandekar (Man in Chopper). Varun Buddhadev (Boy in Chopper). Meenal Kapoor (Woman in Chopper). Hitesh Bharadwaj (Rescue Co-pilot). Kartikeya Narain Tandon (Hariya). Ashok Dhawan (Kaka Jee). Abhash Kumar Makharia (Young Pandit). Ninaad Shaunak Bhatt (Trekker #1). Suraj Paraswani (Trekker #2). Ankit Bhatt (Guy at Tea Shop). Priyadarshan (Tarang). Robin Singh (Suitor) . Lalu Makhija (Cameo)

Language Hindi

Producers Rakesh Bhagwani. Pashan Jal. Salona Bains Joshi. Sonia Kanwar. Abhishek Kapoor. Pragya Kapoor. Ankur Khanna. Sunil Khedekar. Amit Mehta. Abhishek Nayar. Niraj Pamwani. Ajay Rai. Ronnie Screwvala. Yogiraj Shetty. Shubh Shivdasani. Sanaya Irani Zohrabi

Production Guy in the Sky Picture. RSV
